he following benefits:\n"},{"content":"Significantly reduced deployment effort and complexity for Retail HQ components.","pos":[104335,104415]},{"content":"Native deployment to the Microsoft Azure public cloud.","pos":[104425,104479]},{"content":"Improved self-service installation of in-store components to make configuration easier and more intuitive","pos":[104489,104594]},{"content":"Monitor the health of the system, and diagnose errors and issues.","pos":[104638,104703]},{"content":"This functionality requires <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=42636\"&gt;</bpt>System Center 2012 Management Pack for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 R3 CU8 Retail<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/a&gt;</ept>.","pos":[104713,104897],"source":"This functionality requires <a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=42636\">System Center 2012 Management Pack for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 R3 CU8 Retail</a>."},{"content":"Monitoring and diagnostics for Retail components is now available through the <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Operational Insights<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> dashboard in LCS.","pos":[104907,105040],"source":"Monitoring and diagnostics for Retail components is now available through the <strong>Operational Insights</strong> dashboard in LCS."},{"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Operational Insights<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> dashboard is a cloud-based monitoring portal that replaces the need to install the System Center Operations Manager (SCOM) infrastructure.","pos":[105050,105230],"source":"The <strong>Operational Insights</strong> dashboard is a cloud-based monitoring portal that replaces the need to install the System Center Operations Manager (SCOM) infrastructure."},{"content":"Create, configure, download, and install Retail Hardware Station and devices by using self-service.","pos":[105264,105363]},{"content":"By using the installation packager and Enterprise Portal, a user can perform an automated installation and configuration of all components that are required on a particular computer, based on a defined topology.","pos":[105373,105584]},{"content":"Because there are only two installation packages, one for the MPOS client and the other for the Retail Hardware Station component, self-service has reduced the amount of work that is required at every level to install these client components.","pos":[105594,105836]},{"content":"Self-service aims to minimize requirements and make it easier for a user to perform an installation.","pos":[105846,105946]},{"pos":[105980,105985],"content":"Sales","linkify":"Sales","nodes":[{"content":"Sales","pos":[0,5]}]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>What can you do?<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept>","pos":[106029,106062],"source":"<strong>What can you do?</strong>"},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Dynamics AX 2012<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept>","pos":[106072,106105],"source":"<strong>Dynamics AX 2012</strong>"},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Dynamics AX 7.0<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept>","pos":[106115,106147],"source":"<strong>Dynamics AX 7.0</strong>"},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Why is this important?<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept>","pos":[106157,106196],"source":"<strong>Why is this important?</strong>"},{"content":"Get a quick overview of delivery alternatives when you promise orders to customers.","pos":[106230,106313]},{"content":"When there are product availability constraints, and the customer's requested delivery date for one or more products on the order can't be met, the order promising task becomes a challenge.","pos":[106323,106512]},{"content":"To find alternatives that can offset availability and shipping time issues so that the customer’s requested date can be met, or to offer customers a delivery solution that they can accept and trust, the order processor might have to open several forms, each of which offers only a subset of the required information.","pos":[106513,106829]},{"content":"More specifically, one form shows on-hand quantity across sites, another form shows on-hand quantity in the intercompany setting, a third form lets users calculate the earliest available date for one site/variant at a time, and a fourth form shows supply orders.","pos":[106830,107092]},{"content":"Therefore, users don't feel confident that they have considered all the relevant options instead of just choosing an immediate but suboptimal solution.","pos":[107093,107244]},{"content":"Users also don't feel effective, because numerous interruptions occur during the order promising flow as they open and close multiple pages, and combine the insights and options.","pos":[107245,107423]},{"content":"Based on the existing algorithms for delivery date calculation, the <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Delivery alternatives <ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept>page offers a new user experience for order promising:","pos":[107433,107594],"source":"Based on the existing algorithms for delivery date calculation, the <strong>Delivery alternatives </strong>page offers a new user experience for order promising:\n"},{"content":"It consolidates relevant information from multiple forms into one space.","pos":[107604,107676]},{"content":"It offers “ready-made” alternative delivery packages, such as a combination site/warehousing/variant/transport mode, based on the fastest delivery (earliest available date) criterion that the user can choose from.","pos":[107686,107899]},{"content":"It lets the user select options from the simulation interface and transfer them to the sales order line.","pos":[107909,108013]},{"content":"Companies that aspire to provide high customer service while committing to an inventory optimization strategy must be able to promise orders reliably and competitively.","pos":[108034,108202]},{"content":"After all, their customers’ own business requires that products be available on time.","pos":[108203,108288]},{"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Delivery alternatives<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> task page makes the order promising task quicker, easier, and more systematic by identifying and recommending the best alternative order delivery dates in one interactive place.","pos":[108289,108509],"source":" The <strong>Delivery alternatives</strong> task page makes the order promising task quicker, easier, and more systematic by identifying and recommending the best alternative order delivery dates in one interactive place."},{"pos":[108543,108561],"content":"Service management","linkify":"Service management","nodes":[{"content":"Service management","pos":[0,18]}]},{"content":"No new features have been added.","pos":[108562,108594]},{"pos":[108599,108624],"content":"Transportation management","linkify":"Transportation management","nodes":[{"content":"Transportation management","pos":[0,25]}]},{"content":"No new features have been added.","pos":[108625,108657]},{"pos":[108662,108680],"content":"Travel and expense","linkify":"Travel and expense","nodes":[{"content":"Travel and expense","pos":[0,18]}]},{"content":"No new features have been added.","pos":[108681,108713]},{"pos":[108718,108738],"content":"Warehouse management","linkify":"Warehouse management","nodes":[{"content":"Warehouse management","pos":[0,20]}]},{"pos":[109989,110009],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>What can you do?<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**What can you do?**"},{"pos":[110061,110081],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Dynamics AX 2012<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**Dynamics AX 2012**"},{"pos":[110268,110287],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Dynamics AX 7.0<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**Dynamics AX 7.0**"},{"pos":[110428,110454],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Why is this important?<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**Why is this important?**"},{"content":"Download, install, and configure the Warehouse Mobile Devices portal.","pos":[1